        "emailType": "html",
        "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }\n    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35 0%, #F7931E 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; }\n    .header h1 { color: white; margin: 0; }\n    .content { padding: 30px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }\n    .rating-container { margin: 30px 0; }\n    .rating-link { display: inline-block; font-size: 36px; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 5px; }\n    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: #FF6B35; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"header\">\n    <h1>Thank You for Visiting!</h1>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"content\">\n    <p>Hi {{ $json.memberName }},</p>\n    \n    <p>We hope your session at TORCH ATL was amazing! We'd love to hear about your experience.</p>\n    \n    <div class=\"rating-container\">\n      <p><strong>How would you rate your experience?</strong></p>\n      <a href=\"https://torchatl.com/feedback/{{ $json.bookingId }}?rating=5\" class=\"rating-link\">⭐</a>\n      <a href=\"https://torchatl.com/feedback/{{ $json.bookingId }}?rating=4\" class=\"rating-link\">⭐</a>\n      <a href=\"https://torchatl.com/feedback/{{ $json.bookingId }}?rating=3\" class=\"rating-link\">⭐</a>\n      <a href=\"https://torchatl.com/feedback/{{ $json.bookingId }}?rating=2\" class=\"rating-link\">⭐</a>\n      <a href=\"https://torchatl.com/feedback/{{ $json.bookingId }}?rating=1\" class=\"rating-link\">⭐</a>\n    </div>\n    \n    <p>\n      <a href=\"https://torchatl.com/feedback/{{ $json.bookingId }}\" class=\"cta-button\">Leave Detailed Feedback</a>\n    </p>\n    \n    <p>Your feedback helps us improve and serve you better!</p>\n    \n    <hr style=\"margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee;\">\n    \n    <p><strong>Ready to book your next session?</strong></p>\n    <p>\n      <a href=\"https://torchatl.com/book\" class=\"cta-button\">Book Again</a>\n    </p>\n    \n    <p>Thank you for being part of the TORCH community!</p>\n    \n    <p>Warmly,<br><strong>The TORCH ATL Team</strong></p>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
